FramePress - a simple framework for WordPress's plugins
=============
This framework will help you to develop a plugin quickly and easly.
It work as a MVC Framework, Without the Model part, because WP is responsable for those actions
It permit the use of headers, and it has a session emulation

Documentation under construccion
